PURPOSE:-
--------
To show the operation of IP Fragmentation for AODV in wireless scenario.


SCENARIO:-
---------

----- means a wired link


                      1
                     / \
                    /   \
                   /     \
                  2-------3
                  |       |
                  |       |
                  |       |
                  4-------5


CBR is used to send 100 data segments of 2020B from node 5 to node 1.


RUN:-
----
Run '<QUALNET_HOME>/bin/qualnet default.config'.


DESCRIPTION OF THE FILES:-
-------------------------
1. default.app -  QualNet configuration file for application input.
2. default.config - QualNet configuration input file.
3. default.nodes - QualNet configuration file for position of nodes.
4. default.expected.stat - QualNet statistics collection.
5. README - This file.
